section.section:
In determining need under this subsection, the county shall consider:
the failure to meet minimum standards established by the county or the Maryland State Firemen's Association;
the existence or potential existence of an emergency situation as described in § 8-203 of this title;
the age and condition of existing facilities and equipment;
the lack of availability of mutual aid;
any service problems associated with demographic conditions; and
any other relevant factors.
